UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2034
1 organization approved by the department to provide continuing education for
2 certified community health workers. Administrative regulations promulgated
3 pursuant to this subsection shall include requirements for continuing education
4 related to oral health care, infant and maternal health care, and geriatric health care.
5 (5) Notwithstanding any other provision of law to the contrary, an individual shall be
6 eligible to earn college course credit for training, mentorship, and continuing
7 education completed pursuant to subsections (2) and (4) of this section.
